{"tid":1107005,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普眼珠反照「全民公敵」 網上熱爆","createTime":"2019-04-15T02:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T07:39:08.000Z","uid":194012,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"95ae7ca870ac1e65b45399bdae6b003070e4a670","tid":1107005,"uid":194012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:46:11.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普常常當眾對記者怒斥「假新聞」，可謂「不把傳媒放在眼內」。不過美聯社記者近日一張高清照片，放近後可見特朗普的漆黑眼珠反射了白宮記者團的影像，引起熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在自己的記者會上，與美國主流媒體「大戰」過無數回合。那特朗普眼中的媒體是怎樣的呢？從美聯社攝影記者馬丁內斯（Pablo Mart&iacute;nez Monsiv&aacute;is）的一張照片裏或許能找到答案。這張照片拍攝於白宮南面草坪，當天特朗普登上總統專機空軍一號之前在南草坪回答媒體問題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/15/104546_56eee6bd2ba99479e104840adba21dce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F15%2F104546_56eee6bd2ba99479e104840adba21dce.png&h=b32eddd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n與特朗普有宿怨的CNN，也派了主持人摩斯（Jeanne Moos）到場。摩斯問馬丁內斯：「你在特朗普的眼睛裏嗎？」馬丁內斯回答道：「可能吧。」當時他站在媒體隊伍的中間位置，以為自己只是拍了張正常的總統大頭照，未料因為照片超高清，馬丁內斯上載Twitter後，被挖出了「特朗普眼中的傳媒」這個話題。他說：「老實說，我自己也驚了。我下班前上載照片，離開了一會兒，等我再回來的時候，我突然發現『哇』！」<br />\n<br />\n有人讚美照片可以拿個普立茲獎，或有網友稱，從這雙眼睛中看到了不安、害怕，反映特朗普面對他口中的「全民公敵」，也有不快情緒。CNN則從眼中裡發現了當天白宮用來攔媒體記者的繩子。另有網友把之與近日火爆的「黑洞照」合成「黑洞之眼」。<br />\n<br />\n馬丁內斯入行25年，記錄了四屆美國政府，他說：「我拍照的時候準備了三台相機，每台相機上都安了不同的鏡頭，我會根據總統的站位決定使用哪台相機。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/giavVbE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgiavVbE.png&h=4ad762ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5323c7faf3365fe547bcf8c714460b05b01f67a5","tid":1107005,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:49:00.000Z","msg":"真係fake news之最<br />\n一張相任鳩你解讀"},{"pid":"1c5e97432155d264aab905d30ece1f683ce32435","tid":1107005,"uid":194012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/niT11YX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FniT11YX.png&h=ef99b52e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁算yahoo定東網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0e95d37f0ac4a82db01edaf0806572bd24f0c5","tid":1107005,"uid":45252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c5e97432155d264aab905d30ece1f683ce32435","tid":1107005,"uid":194012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/niT11YX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FniT11YX.png&h=ef99b52e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁算yahoo定東網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:33:41.000Z","msg":"why not both"},{"pid":"f3ab629d438221d94758687dfa131335f450c0af","tid":1107005,"uid":3937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c5e97432155d264aab905d30ece1f683ce32435","tid":1107005,"uid":194012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/niT11YX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FniT11YX.png&h=ef99b52e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁算yahoo定東網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /